{"tid":861362,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"而家個心境真係搞唔掂","createTime":"2018-10-14T05:36:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T06:14:41.000Z","uid":193492,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"678a2fa4dff0fa7e175c31ed85e9e58d96edaef3","tid":861362,"uid":193492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T05:36:11.000Z","msg":"班fd喺香港 我去左外國<br />\n我起身佢地瞓<br />\n我瞓佢地嗰邊就係晏晝<br />\nd fd都少左搵我 最大鑊係我開始慣左覺得無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時social既機會就剩係間唔中返學同d隔離位social講一兩句英文<br />\n以前會gel頭襯衫嘗試去keep一個好既外表希望可以喺d女仔面前留下一個好既印象<br />\n而家都無乜所謂 一至五都係咁上下既look 已經開始唔care (但係個樣又應該未去到毒嗰個level既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n更加冇諗過溝女（心態係有女朋友當然開心 冇又無乜所謂）<br />\n有時間都唔想出街<br />\n平時諗既唔係搵工搵intern（或者車既野 早排攞左車牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）就係黎緊幾個星期有咩做 功課project做成點<br />\n有時候d外國fd會叫話一齊去飲杯野hangout 我都冇mood<br />\n而家剩係好想時間快d過 畢業 搵到份工 照顧到自己 父母就ok 呢一生人已經無憾啦<br />\n乜嘢夢想 搵另一半 扑嘢 呢d都冇再去諗<br />\n毒L都起碼會叫春 自怨自艾 有d想要想追求既嘢<br />\n我比佢地更加不濟"},{"pid":"f60e15e1d50c53944f7c6f1b287a650bd535cfbe","tid":861362,"uid":193492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T05:43:26.000Z","msg":"唉屌 人生幾十年 好快過既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1d1cbc8907f978b1483dcbdc02741d3adf91d3","tid":861362,"uid":193492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T05:45:54.000Z","msg":"邊個負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17b95f70a1d67f09a17c66e963f7c9d96b5c8c61","tid":861362,"uid":193492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T05:58:15.000Z","msg":"冇人理添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norm